race.description: Share Bets With Tabtouch Bet Loop Hcp (C1)
race.comment: OCEAN GODDESS (5) missed by 2L over 1200m first-up at this track when closing off soundly from the back of the field. She's likely to get back from the draw once again, though Carbery remains in the saddle and she showed enough there to suggest she's on the cusp of another win. Can get the job done this time. TORA BORA (7) missed by 1.7L at this track last start and the slight rise in trip looks ideal for her again. ZJP's claim comes in handy, she draws well and she's expected to be right in the finish based on her recent figures. RISING FAME (6) sat on the speed and won two back at Bunbury before a disappointing performance as fav 35 days ago. Been freshened since then and maps nicely to bounce back to form. ZALI'S GIFT (9) has been close her past couple and getting back out in trip today is a big tick. Can get the job done this time. BARNEY ROMMEL (4) flew home to win last start and has to be included.
